{"title":"血之验——大水灾有感","authors":["元辉"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"血之验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——大水灾有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛未岁夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句短短的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满感情色彩的壮语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随洪涛声浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响遍所有的华人世界："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血浓于水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着江淮大地地火般灼热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着黄帝陵陵碑般厚重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从四面八方喊出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从无数颗心底喊出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血浓于水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭五千年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香火熏陶，香灰沉淀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭华夏广袤大地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米汁、菜汁的化合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭滚滚长江、莽莽黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和万千涓涓细流的凝缩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血，才如许浓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然背井离乡漂洋过海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然异国异域的水土渗透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血浓度不曾稍减——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如在故土，一如其祖辈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当洪水扫荡半壁河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海内外炎黄子孙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血液都沸腾起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在城镇和村庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在香港的街头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台北的里弄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每条唐人街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每间中国留学生宿舍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人无分老幼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地无分远近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷伸出手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受血浓度之验。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血浓于水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔洪水也检验出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世人血液中的人道因子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水涨水落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水浑水清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场大水灾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更使中国人长了见识。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该记住的，中国人会记住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行动毕竟胜过言辞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}